      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid, Dependable & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Great Pick for Everyday Driving! This used car is in good condition, and it shows! It's been well maintained, runs reliably, and presents nicely inside and out. You'll notice the care that's gone into keeping this vehicle in great shape \u2014 clean interior, smooth ride, and no major issues to worry about. Whether you're commuting daily or planning weekend adventures, this car is ready to deliver. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself \u2014 good cars at honest prices don't last long!",
